content: alefmanvladimir: Created 8 feature request issues this month, all of which have been closed. The issues focused on expanding TON Plugin functionality, including NFT management (#2962), liquidity pool management (#3029), lending and borrowing (#3030), staking (#3031), token price data (#3032), NFT marketplace integration (#3034), wallet creation (#3042), and batch transfer processing (#3043). No code contributions or PR activity during this period.
